posts.name: Chavez Taqueria
posts.note: Outpost of a chain of full-service Mexican grocery stores known for baked goods, meat and takeout. You need to go to one of their store to order tacos from the Chavez Taqueria. When you walk into this small grocery store you can smell the tacos/Mexican foods as soon as you walk in the door. I order remember ordering the Al Pastor and Lengua and a few other Super Tacos.
